{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "08", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "22", "M": "12", "S": "21"}}, "news": [{"title": "Haryana to set up panel to draft proposal for waste-to-energy projects in major cities", "para": "A committee has been formed to draft a model request for proposal for waste-to-energy projects. These projects will be undertaken in major municipal corporations like Gurugram, Faridabad, and Hisar. The initiative aims to strengthen scientific municipal solid waste management. The committee will assess feasibility, identify sites, and frame agreements.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/haryana-plans-waste-to-energy-projects-amid-environmental-concerns/129276269?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-245287/129276269.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Lucknow development body's Park View apartments to have 364 premium flats", "para": "Lucknow Development Authority is launching Park View apartments, a project featuring 364 premium 3BHK flats in Basant Kunj. Registration opens March 7th, with applications exclusively online. The complex will offer modern amenities and is expected to be completed within three years.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/discover-luxurious-3bhk-flats-in-lucknows-park-view-apartments/129275130?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-147371/129275130.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "Amid slump, Hyderabad builders offer Harleys, EVs & gold to push home sales", "para": "Hyderabad developers are offering expensive gifts like Harley Davidsons, EVs, and gold coins to boost sluggish property sales. These incentives, ranging from Rs 3 lakh to Rs 8 lakh, aim to clear unsold inventory amid a market slowdown. Whil